title: Grassy Nook
text: Grassy Nook is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in <a href="Barnstable%20County%2C%20Massachusetts">Barnstable County, Massachusetts</a>. It is located on west of <a href="South%20Orleans%2C%20Massachusetts">South Orleans</a> in the <a href="Brewster%2C%20Massachusetts">Town of Brewster</a>. <a href="Mill%20Hill%20%28Barnstable%20County%2C%20Massachusetts%29">Mill Hill</a> is located northeast of Grassy Nook
